<article><section class=\"page\"><p><figure class=\"right medium\"><img src=\"http://images.techhive.com/images/article/2013/06/platform1-100040380-medium.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\" \" width=\"300\" height=\"184\"/><figcaption>Cue blown mind.</figcaption></figure></p><p><a href=\"http://meatfighter.com/\">Michael Birken</a> has created a <a href=\"http://meatfighter.com/tetrisprinteralgorithm/\">Tetris playing algorithm</a> that creates video game character pixel art. Bananas, you say? Well, it really is.
